title: MemoryCoin - blocks and chainstate
description:
Current (Windows) MemoryCoin Wallet blocks and chainstate, as of 10, July, 2015.

Exit the Wallet utility, and extract to your local directory:

{X}:Users{username}AppDataRoamingMemoryCoin

where {X} is your Windows host drive (usually C), and {username} is the owner of the wallet and executable.

Restart your Wallet utility, and it will sync up, only needing data past 10, July, 2015, and will drastically shorten your reindexing
